data.description: A highly sought after location on the 8th hole of the golf course! 809 Willow Grande Circle has a lot to offer, with wood beams, tall ceilings, heart of pine floors, arched brick doorway, crown molding and detailed woodwork throughout.  This home has tons of storage, to a kitchen with an abondance of granite countertops, an office and a full large upstairs room with a full bathroom.  You don't want to miss out on this rare find!  From the moment you walk in you will feel at home! Call your favorite realtor today!
